Sir, what are we doing at a place like this?

56
00:04:31,271 --> 00:04:33,773
Our plan is to bust into a bank
and get some money.

57
00:04:33,773 --> 00:04:37,709
If we flutter about too much, we might
attract people's attention.

58
00:04:44,917 --> 00:04:46,919
Nothing has changed.

59
00:04:46,919 --> 00:04:48,614
It's exactly the same as before.

60
00:04:53,293 --> 00:04:54,760
Welcome!

61
00:05:00,967 --> 00:05:02,468
What can I serve you today?

62
00:05:02,468 --> 00:05:04,203
Zaru, two of them.

63
00:05:04,203 --> 00:05:05,670
Sure!

64
