Oh, I can't eat any more.

65
00:05:10,743 --> 00:05:12,370
Eat! Eat with guts.

66
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,608
I understand, Sir.

67
00:05:15,148 --> 00:05:18,208
You intend to rob this place before
we do the bank, don't you?

68
00:05:18,685 --> 00:05:21,415
Why didn't you say so?

69
00:05:22,555 --> 00:05:26,693
Excuse me, but are you related to
the lady who owns this place?

70
00:05:26,693 --> 00:05:30,196
Sir, do you know my mother?

71
00:05:30,196 --> 00:05:32,790
Not really.

72
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:35,234
Her daughter...

73
00:05:35,234 --> 00:05:37,031
I guess I saw a little girl back then.

74
00:05:43,176 --> 00:05:45,303
She... My mother passed away.

75
00:05:46,045 --> 00:05:47,672
There was a car accident.

76
00:05:50,850 --> 00:05:53,519
Sir, let's hurry up!

77
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:55,350
I will make a chance.

78
00:05:57,123 --> 00:05:58,658
Sorry to keep you waiting.

79
00:05:58,658 --> 00:06:01,286
Wow, now it's time to eat!

80
00:06:23,616 --> 00:06:28,144
Lady, do you intend to get
paid for food like this?

81
00:06:29,188 --> 00:06:32,225
That's right! We should get
paid for eating this.

82
00:06:32,225 --> 00:06:33,214
Ouch!

83
00:06:34,794 --> 00:06:36,529
It hurts.

84
00:06:36,529 --> 00:06:37,996
Sir, what did you do to me?

85
00:06:40,233 --> 00:06:44,604
Lady, nowadays, Chinese Ramen noodles
are very popular among people,

86
00:06:44,604 --> 00:06:49,234
but I believe the Japanese soba noodle
contains the soul of the Japanese.

87
00:06:49,942 --> 00:06:51,910
However, I'm sorry to tell you,
but this soba...

88
00:06:52,578 --> 00:06:54,113
It's already dead.

89
00:06:54,113 --> 00:06:55,580
Dead?

90
00:06:57,583 --> 00:07:00,119
Excuse me, Sir, but isn't it a little rude

91
00:07:00,119 --> 00:07:03,520
to say things like that without
eating even a bite?

92
00:07:04,590 --> 00:07:07,427
I can tell that by just picking up
the noodles with chopsticks.

93
00:07:07,427 --> 00:07:10,430
These soba noodles are different from
Sarashina-Soba powder,

94
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:15,034
