are not strong enough.

97
00:07:21,941 --> 00:07:24,637
Therefore, if you try to pick up a noodle
with chopsticks, it falls apart.

98
00:07:25,211 --> 00:07:27,680
The dipping sauce and the noodles
are not well matched at all.

99
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,615
In order to make these noodles taste good,

100
00:07:29,615 --> 00:07:31,742
the dipping sauce should have
a thicker taste.

101
00:07:32,151 --> 00:07:34,253
The essence of the dipping sauce
needs more time,

102
00:07:34,253 --> 00:07:36,823
and the dried tuna flake for the broth
needs to be shaved thicker,

103
