then the sauce might be better.

104
00:07:39,659 --> 00:07:43,026
Only a cockroach would eat
soba noodles like these.

105
00:07:45,631 --> 00:07:47,326
I'm a cockroach.

106
00:07:51,437 --> 00:07:52,572
Mr. Gondo!

107
00:07:52,572 --> 00:07:53,706
Oh, what a scene!

108
00:07:53,706 --> 00:07:56,976
It's a very rare occasion for me to see
customers in this restaurant.

109
00:07:56,976 --> 00:07:58,443
What do you want?

110
00:07:59,045 --> 00:08:03,316
My mother took care of this place very well
and I don't intend to give it up at all.

111
00:08:03,316 --> 00:08:05,318
Please calm down.

112
00:08:05,318 --> 00:08:07,954
Anyway, it's too hot inside this restaurant.

113
00:08:07,954 --> 00:08:10,389
Why don't you take off your clothes?

114
