Sir!

122
00:08:46,092 --> 00:08:47,360
Idiots.

123
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,761
Well, shall we go?

124
00:08:48,761 --> 00:08:50,888
Sir, it's time, isn't it?

125
00:08:55,601 --> 00:08:57,091
Please wait!

126
00:08:59,705 --> 00:09:02,542
Please accept me as your pupil.

127
00:09:02,542 --> 00:09:05,375
I desperately want to create
the best soba in Japan.

128
00:09:05,945 --> 00:09:08,914
