147
00:10:04,337 --> 00:10:05,905
No, no!

148
00:10:05,905 --> 00:10:09,033
Use more power and lean with
your entire weight!

149
00:10:11,010 --> 00:10:12,443
What a mean guy!

150
00:10:13,045 --> 00:10:14,547
No!

151
00:10:14,547 --> 00:10:16,415
In order to create soba noodles
with a good consistency,

152
00:10:16,415 --> 00:10:18,007
