Look what they've done!

162
00:11:06,098 --> 00:11:07,867
Ryo, they're the guys who came here earlier.

163
00:11:07,867 --> 00:11:09,732
It's too much! Too cruel!

164
00:11:10,069 --> 00:11:11,536
I won't give up!

165
00:11:12,738 --> 00:11:14,306
I will not give up because of
something like this!

166
00:11:14,306 --> 00:11:15,773
Absolutely not!

167
00:11:21,147 --> 00:11:23,115
Athletic Club

168
00:11:32,858 --> 00:11:38,763
Scattering sweat, fresh bodies, this is the
extreme mokkori I've been seeking!

169
00:11:39,165 --> 00:11:42,868
Oh, God, I thank you that you
gave me life in this world!

170
00:11:42,868 --> 00:11:45,996
Well, well, Mika!

171
00:11:49,075 --> 00:11:51,635
Fight, fight, fight...

172
00:11:52,078 --> 00:11:54,603
Fight, fight, fight...

173
00:11:55,081 --> 00:11:57,777
Fight, fight, fight...

174
00:12:03,456 --> 00:12:06,892
Finally, I finished cleaning up the trash.

175
00:12:06,892 --> 00:12:10,293
Anyway, I wonder how long
he intends to stay here?

176
00:12:17,203 --> 00:12:20,072
Last night, you recognized us
while you were watching TV,

177
00:12:20,072 --> 00:12:22,040
and you changed the channel, didn't you?

178
00:12:22,508 --> 00:12:23,743
I would like to ask you why.

179
00:12:23,743 --> 00:12:24,643
I don't know.

180
00:12:24,643 --> 00:12:27,847
Just like you can tell whether the soba
noodles are good or bad at a glance,

181
00:12:27,847 --> 00:12:30,816
I can tell whether the person is really a
bad person or not, just by looking at him.

182
00:12:30,816 --> 00:12:32,918
I think there's a story behind
what you're doing here.

183
00:12:32,918 --> 00:12:36,217
You look a little odd because you
concentrate on Mika so much.

184
00:12:39,558 --> 00:12:40,659
Obligations...

185
00:12:40,659 --> 00:12:43,129
I am deeply indebted to her mother.

186
00:12:43,129 --> 00:12:46,758
A long time ago, I killed someone because
of an obligation from my gambler's life.

187
00:12:47,266 --> 00:12:50,133
Well, it's been ten years ago now.

188
00:12:50,870 --> 00:12:55,775
I had been running away from the
police, running and running,

189
00:12:55,775 --> 00:12:57,504
and the place I ended up was
the restaurant, Shirako-Ya.

190
00:13:10,189 --> 00:13:15,058
That lady was just beautiful.
She was there just being beautiful.

191
00:13:39,952 --> 00:13:40,919
Damn!

192
00:13:44,523 --> 00:13:46,792
Honestly speaking, at that time,
I couldn't decide what to do.

193
00:13:46,792 --> 00:13:49,989
The reason I jumped in there
was to find hostages.

194
00:13:55,534 --> 00:13:57,603
Anyway, I lost.

195
00:13:57,603 --> 00:13:59,070
I don't know why.

196
00:13:59,839 --> 00:14:02,706
